# Top-level Functions — basic

## add

```dart
add(int a, int b) → int
```

Source: lib/src/functions.dart:4:4

A simple top-level function.

Returns the sum of [a] and [b].

```dart
int add(int a, int b) => a + b;
```

---

## capitalize

```dart
capitalize(String input) → String
```

Source: lib/src/functions.dart:28:33

Capitalizes [input].

```dart
String capitalize(String input) {
  if (input.isEmpty) {
    return input;
  }
  return input[0].toUpperCase() + input.substring(1);
}
```

---

## identity

```dart
